ntroduce Magnitsky-style sanctions, which are geared at ensuring that those who commit human rights abuses are not allowed to enter countries. ​Restrictions would be placed on them. I am sure that the Magnitsky sanctions regime will play an important part in the overall mix as we consider our human rights policy globally"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"contemplating, 剛睇咗twit。但英國佬。。。。<br />\n嗰政府俾支共入囇差幾時俾人中出咁滯，希望美國佬可以整翻醒佢"},{"pid":"68611c85f8b21da97c6cb6232669280c5d6e8b38","tid":1833054,"uid":270532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"做左先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用華為你叫人點信英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328c8fafb61250abf370a32355f6d34af697f4ad","tid":1833054,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"考慮! fuckoff 啦, 中國英倫省!"},{"pid":"4abd6653c889b472bd3bbbe2ebbe6ad78187b020","tid":1833054,"uid":146805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"日落帝國confirmed"},{"pid":"50f2d95b925830a90912de8baba6d224d12c5532","tid":1833054,"uid":63326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"日落帝國算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101738af050d76145810fd5391dae4b871f2515d","tid":1833054,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42347072b7036343de99547ae89536f5defad00","tid":1833054,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"做野再講"},{"pid":"c363ed6762aad989053d03267d4957c4ec0db38d","tid":1833054,"uid":233586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:33:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d53f99943983feadfed918e3de7